definitions.definition: ( Latin America , Philippines ) An open tract of ground ; a plain , especially one which is moist and fertile , such as those used for growing tobacco .

main_definition: ( Latin America , Philippines ) An open tract of ground ; a plain , especially one which is moist and fertile , such as those used for growing tobacco .

definitions.definition: A measurement of the sensitivity of the value of an option to changes in the implied volatility of the price of the underlying asset .

main_definition: ( finance ) A measurement of the sensitivity of the value of an option to changes in the implied volatility of the price of the underlying asset .
